Coney Island: West 12th Street, east side, at the Bowery. One of the thrills at Coney Island (the Wonder Wheel). This is a set of two views.

July 4, 1936.
View 2: 1938.

P. L. Sperr.

(3)
The same, another view.

1928.

George L. Balgue.
title: Islands - Coney Island - Wonder wheel - [Brooklyn: 12th Street - Bowery.]
